[[!meta title="""Smuxi 0.9 "The Fix" Release"""]]

It's finally here! We're proud to announce the new version of Smuxi, release
0.9 "***The Fix***". During the development, [19 bug reports][bugs] and
[8 feature requests][features] in [235 commits][commits] were worked on making
this release a major feature and major bugfix release.

Notable highlights in this release are:

### Enhanced User Interface ###

 * Smuxi Symbolic Icon Theme (George Karavasilev)
 * [smarter nick completion][558]: prefere last active nicks for tab completion
   (Ondrej Hošek)
 * [smarter nicklist][432]: predict and set useful width for the nicklist
 * Mac OS X: [fixed copy/paste command key shortcuts][845]

