### Text Frontend Enhancements ###

 * STFL frontend on OpenBSD
 * [STFL Topic Support][844] (Ondrej Hošek)
 * [STFL proper line wrapping][849] (Ondrej Hošek)
 * STFL color support

### JabbR Support ###

 * [SignalR's JabbR Support][843]
   * /join command, highlight support

### Twitter Enhancements ###

 * [Twitter v1.1][872]: Twitter removed their v1 API on the 11th June which
   broke Smuxi and many other Twitter application from that date on. Smuxi works
   with Twitter again after porting it to the v1.1 API.

### XMPP (Beta) Enhacenments ###

 * XMPP/Jabber Contacts
   * Contacts can be renamed from context menu
 * [XMPP Rewrite][819] (Oliver Schneider)
 * Added favicon mappings of famous Jabber servers: jabber.org, jabber.de,
   jabber.at, jabber.ccc.de and jabber.gmx.net

### IRC Enhancements ###

 * [IRC passive channel sync][787]
 * [IRC UTF-8 recode][288]: automatic recode of UTF-8 characters when needed
   (Ondrej Hošek)
 * [IRC channel usermodes][161]: Owner, Half-Op and Admin modes support
   (Ondrej Hošek)

### Updated Translations ###

Smuxi should now be in your language, including:

 * Initial complete Portuguese (Brazil) (Leonardo Pires Felix)
 * Initial complete Finnish (Kalle Kaitala)
 * French (Clément Bourgeois)
 * Czech (Ondřej Hošek)
 * Chinese Simp (Dean Lee)
 * Swedish (Jimmie Elvenmark)
 * Danish (Joe Hansen)
 * German (Bianca Mix)

### Behind the Scenes ###

 * Mono 3.0 Support

